HOW TO USE YOUR TIME SELECTOR: Turn dial until present
standard time lines up with city in which you are located.
Standard time in other cities is automatically indicated.
Always read clockwise. Deduct one day when passing
through International Date Line. Add one hour for Daylight
Saving Time. Remember that you move into the next
day when passing through midnight.
